@prefix : <http://example.org/ontology-cyber#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix xml: <http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

<http://example.org/ontology-cyber> rdf:type owl:Ontology .

### Classes

:Threat rdf:type owl:Class .
:Asset rdf:type owl:Class .
:Vulnerability rdf:type owl:Class .

### Object Properties

:affects rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:domain :Threat ;
    rdfs:range :Asset .

:exploits rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:domain :Threat ;
    rdfs:range :Vulnerability .
